description:
MAGENTA ARCADE is a finger-based top-down shooter brought to you by Long Hat House. Become a god! Your finger is a weapon, but also your greatest weakness. Know when to touch the screen to attack or retract to defend yourself!

The cycle of wishes is a sacred ritual for the people! It is where you give out wishes for them. During many cycles peace reigned in your lands, but everything changed when Ivo Magenta made his last wish. 

Now, disaster emerges, and you have to sleep until the next cycle. When you wake up, everything depends on you! Use your finger to shoot him and his minions down, the world's order is now in your hands! Literally!

Long Hat House is an indie developer studio based in Belo Horizonte, Brazil.

